---

<style>
.author-bios {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}
.author-bios h2 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: black;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
}
.author-bio {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    background: #f8f8f8;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
}
.author-bio img {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
}
.author-details {
    flex: 1;
}
.author-details h3 {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: black;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}
.author-details p {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: gray;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.author-details .social-media {
    margin-top: 10px;
}
.author-details .social-media a {
    margin-right: 10px;
    color: #00BFFF;
    font-size: 18px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
}
.author-details .social-media a:hover {
    color: black;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .author-bio {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .author-details {
        text-align: center;
    }
}
</style>

<section class="author-bios">
    <h2>Meet the Authors</h2>
    <div class="author-bio">
        <img src="/path/to/author-photo.jpg" alt="Author Photo">
        <div class="author-details">
            <h3>Jane Doe</h3>
            <p>Fitness Enthusiast</p>
            <p>Jane Doe is a fitness enthusiast with over 10 years of experience in home workouts and training. Follow her on social media for more tips and guides.</p>
            <div class="social-media">
                <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Facebook</a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitter</a>
                <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Add more author bios as needed -->
</section>